| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2859 — Mass File Rename (malas)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 153e299a-ea12-5fd2-9686-369af74a6687"
index=*
| where (file_path="*.encrypted" OR file_path="*.locked" OR file_path="*.ransom")
